			<h1>Gain the Edge <span class="goAwaySooner"><br /></span>on Device Configuration and Deployment</h1>
		</div>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-lg-12">
				<p>The all new Edge device from ThinManager provides a turnkey solution for configuring and deploying the world's most advanced thin client management system. The Edge comes preloaded with Windows Server 2016, TS Cals, pre-activated RDS licenses and, of course, ThinManager.</p>

				<p>The Edge device incorporates new ThinManager plug-n-play technology which auto-senses ThinManager-Ready devices and pre-configures them for immediate deployment. The Edge device also auto-senses other Edge devices so that redundancy is automatically enabled when connected additional Edge devices to your network.</p>
