				<p>The Edge server supports ThinManager's powerful new virtualization technology (DRIVE) Deployable Resource in Virtualized Environment. Using the Edge configuration wizard, administrator's can easily virtualize their Remote Desktop Server(s) without incurring any additional costs for a third part virtualization solution.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-3 col-md-offset-1">
				<h3>The Edge of the Future</h3>
				<p>Centralized, client-based deployment is now widely accepted as the best way to deploy and manage plant floor applications and devices. The new ThinManager Edge now makes using thin technology as easy as opening the box, plugging it in and turning it on. Don't waste your time and money piecing together a thin client solution. Get ThinManager and gain the Edge on your competition today.</p>
